<h2>Step 4: Structure Content with Clear Headers</h2>
<p>Google uses your <a href="/blog/blog-post-structure-seo/">heading structure</a> to understand what each section covers. A clean H2/H3 hierarchy signals where answers live.</p>
<p><strong>Header rules:</strong></p>
